overview: In June 2012 TNT celebrated their 30th anniversary with a concert where they performed songs from their whole career, from heavy hymns like "Seven Seas" to hard rock hits like "10,000 Lovers and "Intuition". On stage they were joined by the Trondheim Symphony Orchestra as well as contributions from all vocalists from the band's illustrious 30 year career.
tagline: TNT's anniversary concert with the Trondheim Symphony Orchestra!
title: TNT 30th Anniversary 1982-2012: Live In Concert
